column1: Results from the 2003 IBSA World Powerlifting Championships
August 5th - 6th at the 2nd IBSA World Blind Championships and Games
Women's Junior: Tatiana Briceno, Venezuela, Wilks = 359.0
Women's Senior: Silvia Alba, Spain, Wilks = 313.8
Men's Junior: Serguei Chatalov, Russia, Wilks = 444.1
Men's Senior: Alexei Moukhametov, Russia, Wilks = 422.8
Men's Master: Stephen Brown, United Kingdom, Wilks = 396.1
John Baxter Most Improved Lifter Award
Adam Bury, from 420.0k to 512.5k for a 92.5k improvement
